title: No PhD? No Friends? [Q&A] Earnest answers to insincere questions.
description: A Q&A of sorts (with some meta-Q&A commentary).  "Why doesn't Eisel already have a PhD?" & "Why didn't you keep more of your friends (from high-school, or other, earlier chapters of your life) as you moved from one chapter to the next?"
